[info] MovableComponentSpec:
[info] A MovableComponent 
[info] - should have a well-defined starting Id
[info] - should preserves its id when casted down
[info] - should have a well-defined starting position
[info] - should have a well-defined starting rotation angles
[info] - should change its (X,Y) position when asked to
[info] - should change its (X,Y,Z) position when asked to
[info] - should change its (X,Y,Z, rotX, rotY, rotZ) when asked to
